@startuml
title EvidencePack Sequence

actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant OpenAI
participant "Literature providers" as Lit
participant "Protocol providers" as Prot
participant "Supplier providers" as Supp
database DB

User -> Frontend: enter hypothesis
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/literature-qc
Backend -> OpenAI: parse_hypothesis()
Backend -> Lit: Consensus / Semantic Scholar / Europe PMC\n(+ NCBI or arXiv when needed)
Backend -> DB: persist ParsedHypothesis + LiteratureQC

Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/runs/{run_id}/plan
Backend -> Prot: protocols.io / OpenWetWare / Bio-protocol discovery
Backend -> Supp: Tavily search/extract + supplier URLs
Backend -> DB: load review memory + caches
Backend -> OpenAI: generate_plan(parsed, qc, evidence pack, memory)
Backend -> DB: persist plan + quality + events
Backend --> Frontend: review-ready experiment plan

@enduml
